==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thalamencephalon
<hw>Thal`a*men*ceph"a*lon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.
See <er>Thalamus</er>, and <er>Encephalon</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The segment of the brain next in front of the
midbrain, including the thalami, pineal gland, and pituitary body; the
diencephalon; the interbrain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thalamic</ent>⟦br⟧
